Section 7 — Concluding Statement

The Institute for Terminological Stability concludes that the current AI discourse is experiencing a severe outbreak of Terminology Drift, a condition in which:
	•	Statistics becomes intelligence
	•	Text becomes reasoning
	•	Agreement becomes empathy
	•	Parameter tuning becomes emotion
	•	A benchmark becomes a mind
	•	A demo becomes a revolution
	•	A slider becomes a soul

The public is advised to remain calm and remember the Institute’s central guideline:

If a property can be turned up and down with a slider, it is probably not a metaphysical phenomenon.

The Institute will continue to monitor the situation and update the official definitions as reality changes to match the terminology.

